  "root_text": {
    "sn45.110:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 45.110–114 ",
    "sn45.110:0.2": "10. Dutiyagaṅgāpeyyālavagga ",
    "sn45.110:0.3": "Dutiyādisamuddaninnasutta ",
    "sn45.110:1.1": "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yamunā nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; ",
    "sn45.110:1.2": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu …pe… ",
    "sn45.110:1.3": "dutiyaṁ. ",
    "sn45.111:1.1": "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, aciravatī nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; ",
    "sn45.111:1.2": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu …pe… ",
    "sn45.111:1.3": "tatiyaṁ. ",
    "sn45.112:1.1": "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, sarabhū nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; ",
    "sn45.112:1.2": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu …pe… ",
    "sn45.112:1.3": "catutthaṁ. ",
    "sn45.113:1.1": "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahī nadī samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; ",
    "sn45.113:1.2": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu …pe… ",
    "sn45.113:1.3": "pañcamaṁ. ",
    "sn45.114:1.1": "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yā kācimā mahānadiyo, seyyathidaṁ—",
    "sn45.114:1.2": "gaṅgā, yamunā, aciravatī, sarabhū, mahī, sabbā tā samuddaninnā samuddapoṇā samuddapabbhārā; ",
    "sn45.114:1.3": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bhāvento ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. ",
    "sn45.114:1.4": "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bhāvento ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro? ",
    "sn45.114:1.5": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṁ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṁ dosavinayapariyosānaṁ mohavinayapariyosānaṁ …pe… sammāsamādhiṁ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṁ dosavinayapariyosānaṁ mohavinayapariyosānaṁ. ",
    "sn45.114:1.6": "Evaṁ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bhāvento ariyaṁ aṭṭhaṅgikaṁ maggaṁ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. ",
    "sn45.114:1.7": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. ",
    "sn45.114:1.8": "(Rāgavinayadvādasakī dutiyakī samuddaninnanti.) "
  },
